change.subject: soc: nexell: nxs_dev: Add NXS_CONTROL_STATUS
change.commitMessage:
soc: nexell: nxs_dev: Add NXS_CONTROL_STATUS
This patch adds new nxs_control_type named NXS_CONTROL_STATUS. NXS_CONTROL_STATUS is needed to get specific status of each nxs_dev like hdmi connection status etc. Also, status field is added to nxs_control structure.
